{"tid":115213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"安徽化工廠爆炸 死亡人數增為16人","createTime":"2017-02-10T11:35:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-10T12:52:49.000Z","uid":57303,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ea0d97c1314f64710670533b8d13229e266e8d52","tid":115213,"uid":57303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T11:35:48.000Z","msg":"(據中廣新聞報導)中國大陸安徽省上週五一座化工廠爆炸，死亡人數已經增加到16人，另外24人受傷送醫治療。大陸「當安化學集團」在安徽省一座兩層樓的化工廠上週五發生爆炸意外，廠房被夷為平地，目前已經發現十六具屍體，其中十人的身分已經確認，但是另外六人的屍體焦黑難辨。目前還不清楚爆炸發生時，工廠內有多少人。<br />\n<br />\n初步調查指出，廠房內至少有四噸炸藥，意外可能是由於工人作業時不慎將炸藥引爆。這是華東地區一星期內發生的第二起工廠意外，上星期，浙江一座化工廠爆炸造成一人受傷兩人失蹤。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/6/6/19/n1355403.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F6%2F6%2F19%2Fn1355403.htm&d=JinSrGH%2FoctmVpTuEhnihJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=3ecd17c1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/6/6/19/n1355403.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a7b604be58a6ba79c1f3f9e36c5b906ea45b3038","tid":115213,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T11:36:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/10/193646_19a5be1012f87524375a600952cddd62.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F10%2F193646_19a5be1012f87524375a600952cddd62.jpg&h=631fa12d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"698217b3c5d192cb8222cc79a64a555f15fe8eb6","tid":115213,"uid":42434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T11:50:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"958bf8b2b9211133b898c35abbca0718219ce7f9","tid":115213,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T12:11:55.000Z","msg":"假新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"944cceabffe15cbfaa74f4c43209437333bf062b","tid":115213,"uid":230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T12:15:56.000Z","msg":"Magic number 37呢？"},{"pid":"b6f6a750f31e915eacd16df4a0783b8b2db83d1f","tid":115213,"uid":10680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T12:16:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7c3d60cd85f6dd31bebfb9198e715e90bd346484","tid":115213,"uid":35914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T12:21:41.000Z","msg":"爆到咁都係得16人，支那真係地大"},{"pid":"d57073149b75f244eb549a2d3b1a785adb83db77","tid":115213,"uid":33916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T12:23:55.000Z","msg":"放心, 點撚樣都唔會過36"},{"pid":"c10e53ba8d10943eb884aae20bf09ffb6801cc9a","tid":115213,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T12:26:34.000Z","msg":"蒸發左既唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ef24c5d02cd1011cbc7cffa6c1e40830e5fd975","tid":115213,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T12:52:49.000Z","msg":"最多35"}]}